title: Social media injunction unravels plans to protect 2024 elections
description: The companies and the government spent years expanding efforts to combat election interference after the 2016 vote;  the ruling undoes much of that.

title: How an AI-written Star Wars story created chaos at Gizmodo
description: A Gizmodo story on Star Wars, generated by artificial intelligence, was riddled with errors. The irony that the problem happened at a tech publication was undeniable.
